title: DDD Melbourne 2024
eventShortDescription:
DDD Melbourne is an inclusive non-profit conference for the software community. Our goal is to create an approachable event that appeals to the whole community, especially people who usually don’t have the opportunity to attend, or speak at, conferences.

Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this event.
